fields.name: Mini
fields.description: The mini session includes 60 minutes photography outdoors with you and your family. Your choice of 15 digital images edited and retouched and sent as digital downloads.

fields.name: Standard
fields.description:
The standard photoshoot includes 3 hours photography in the studio.
Your choice of 40 digital images edited and retouched and sent as digital downloads and a 10x8 inch mounted professional print.

fields.name: Premium
fields.description:
The premium photoshoot includes 6 hours photography on 3 different locations.
Your choice of 70 digital images edited and retouched and sent as digital downloads and five 10x8 inch mounted professional print.
Styling and make-up is included as well.
